
************************************************************************
*****  LANDAU WANG ALGORITHM FOR THE ALPHA-3-STATES MODEL **************
************************************************************************

CONTENTS of the 'wang-landau' folder: --------------------------------

  'Code' (subfolder):
    'main.f90'
    'module.f90'
    'input.dat' (output name: nom, size: N, random seed: iseed, initial modifier: ln_f, 
                 alpha value: alpha, number of MC attempts: MCtot, flatness tolerance: tol, 
                 modifier threshold: eps, numerical tolerance: eps2))
    'r1279.o', 'ran2.o', secs.o' (random generator files)

  'Images' (subfolder):
    'ln_g_N10', 'ln_g_N12', 'ln_g_N14', 'ln_g_N16' (Plots of the ln(states density(E)) .vs. E)
    
  'Scripts'
    'ln_g.gnu' (For the output visualization)


COMPILING INSTRUCTIONS (from local folder 'Code'): ------------------------------------------------

gfortran -g -fcheck=all -Wall -fbacktrace module.f90 main.f90 r1279.o ran2.o secs.o -o main.exe

./main.exe (execution)
    

